r\n全裸で目隠しをして両手を吊るされている花奏の姿があった。\r\n\r\n戸惑う西田は、それでも動揺を隠しつつ無言のままカメラを回す。\r\n\r\nレンズの先には淫乱メス豚へと完璧に調教され、\r\nオマ●コにバイブ、アナルには肉棒をぶっ刺し喘ぐその姿を\r\nライブ配信で視聴者たちにも見られていた。"}],"crt":[{"id":87263,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/52/ac/87263_crt_RwuW1.jpg","name":"天河花奏","desc":"朝比奈幸"}],"staff":[{"id":3385,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/13/1f/3385_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"アニメアンテナ委員会","desc":"制作"},{"id":11933,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1c/d3/11933_prsn_9WE98.jpg","name":"セブン","desc":"补间动画"},{"id":3385,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/13/1f/3385_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"アニメアンテナ委員会","desc":"製作"},{"id":38250,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/07/28/38250_prsn_jTEtm.jpg","name":"オコイス8番","desc":"制作协力"},{"id":2100,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c6/9f/2100_prsn_67wnT.jpg","name":"むらかみてるあき","desc":"制片人"},{"id":38249,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3f/37/38249_prsn_aLLl4.jpg","name":"Pak Pro","desc":"补间动画"},{"id":38248,"image":"","name":"梁守仁裕","desc":"音响监督"},{"id":38260,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d0/da/38260_prsn_hG3aj.jpg","name":"Media Bank","desc":"製作"},{"id":11749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c5/fd/11749_prsn_m4RJJ.jpg","name":"WHITE BEAR","desc":"製作"},{"id":38255,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c0/67/38255_prsn_S40rp.jpg","name":"キャプテン秋山","desc":"企画"},{"id":38259,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6e/2b/38259_prsn_zEMm5.jpg","name":"新海コウキ","desc":"剪辑"},{"id":38249,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3f/37/38249_prsn_aLLl4.jpg","name":"Pak Pro","desc":"背景美术"},{"id":38249,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/3f/37/38249_prsn_aLLl4.jpg","name":"Pak Pro","desc":"原画"},{"id":1979,"image":"","name":"荒木英樹","desc":"作画监督"},{"id":1979,"image":"","name":"荒木英樹","desc":"人物设定"},{"id":33793,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/94/3b/33793_prsn_LWxMk.jpg","name":"もんぷち","desc":"人物原案"},{"id":1979,"image":"","name":"荒木英樹","desc":"分镜"},{"id":38247,"image":"","name":"可動命","desc":"脚本"},{"id":1979,"image":"","name":"荒木英樹","desc":"导演"},{"id":29109,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/40/35/29109_prsn_iTdT1.jpg","na